theorem Topology.compl_boundary_eq_union_interiors {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A : Set X} :
    (closure A \ interior A)ᶜ = interior A ∪ interior (Aᶜ) := by
  -- Start with an existing description of the complement of the boundary.
  have h₁ :=
    Topology.compl_boundary_eq_union_interior_compl_closure (X := X) (A := A)
  -- Express `((closure A)ᶜ)` in terms of `interior (Aᶜ)`.
  have h₂ : (closure A)ᶜ = interior (Aᶜ) := by
    simpa using
      (Topology.interior_compl_eq_compl_closure (X := X) (A := A)).symm
  -- Substitute and conclude.
  simpa [h₂] using h₁
